content.rendered:
Directed by Ivan Ayr.

Written by Kislay Kislay.

Cast Geetika Vidya Ohlyan(Soni). Saloni Batra(Kalpana). Vikas Shukla(Naveen). Mohit Chauhan(Sandeep). Himanshu Kohli(Navy Officer). Gauri Chakraborty(Huma). Mohinder Gujral(Mummy ji). Upasya Goswami(J.B). Simrat Kaur(Nishu). Dimple Kaur(Daisy). Prateek Pachauri(Govind (as Prateek Pachori)). Kalpana Jha(Landlord’s wife). Samar(ASI Chauhan) . Ishu(Stalker). Prateek Pachori(Govind). Punit Tiwari(Second Navy Officer)

Language Hindi.

Producers Kimsi Singh.

Production Jabberwockee Talkie.
